  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK866">
<l>kāṇāc ciṉattāṉ kaḻiperuṅ kāmattāṉ</l>
<l>pēṇāmai pēṇap paṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Highly to be desired is the hatred of him whose anger is blind, and whose lust increases beyond measure.</l>
            </lg>
